{"tid":2117800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王國興挺郭偉強 市民斥「收皮」","createTime":"2020-07-21T05:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T06:09:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80e4ef0004c33a8d0e7dc4ffb21facba99f582f1","tid":2117800,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/RKOEDGZZDP5R6WZH2TP7PMLS3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FRKOEDGZZDP5R6WZH2TP7PMLS3M%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=e6a241ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FRKOEDGZZDP5R6WZH2TP7PMLS3M%2F&h=123dddcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/RKOEDGZZDP5R6WZH2TP7PMLS3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n王國興挺郭偉強 市民斥「收皮」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qEOd8_KC3tF8Hd6Zp4eJyr0g4OU=/918x635/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZNT4TOQSKYMTMV3OAWHB23QO2A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqEOd8_KC3tF8Hd6Zp4eJyr0g4OU%3D%2F918x635%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZNT4TOQSKYMTMV3OAWHB23QO2A.gif&h=b0e5eb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王國興（左）聲援郭偉強（中），更以「勇士」等形容對方。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派多名候選人昨日。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強被問到向陳志全施襲一事時，聲言當時只是令立會保安和陳志全「有合理距離」，又稱不能評論得太仔細，拒透露至今有否收到法庭傳票，只說：「呢個大家唔使擔心，呢個我委託咗律師嘅團隊跟進。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟競選口號「硬淨」<br />\n<br />\n上屆超區敗陣的王國興現身發言時，指立會需要如郭偉強一樣「勇士」、「鬥士」和「戰士」，大讚郭在立法會敢於與「反中亂港」議員「搏鬥」，其間有巿民途經時多次向王高喊：「你收皮啦！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"891c2c975d3aa5b79d5c410d49a5e290b7c6e601","tid":2117800,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"日以繼夜、夜以繼日，再日以繼夜、夜以繼日......"},{"pid":"25d51f0a883ca59345abd1bc16a944c2190414b2","tid":2117800,"uid":342855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjZfCZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjZfCZC.jpg&h=80d87e18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"036591c369bbec2c23d22884af55c393629199dc","tid":2117800,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}